<h2>You gained a new follower</h2>

<p>Hi <%= typeof name !== "undefined" && name ? name : (typeof vendorName !== "undefined" && vendorName ? vendorName : "there") %>,</p>

<p>
  <strong><%= followerName || "A shopper" %></strong> just followed your seller profile
  <% if (vendorName) { %>
    for <strong><%= vendorName %></strong>
  <% } %>
  on Piessang.
</p>

<p>
  You can open your seller notifications to keep track of new followers and other account activity.
</p>

<p style="margin-top: 16px;">
  <a href="<%= dashboardUrl %>" style="display:inline-block;padding:10px 16px;border-radius:8px;background:#202020;color:#fff;text-decoration:none;">
    Open seller notifications
  </a>
</p>

<p style="margin-top: 16px;">
  If the button does not work, copy this link into your browser:<br/>
  <%= dashboardUrl %>
</p>

<p style="margin-top: 20px;">
  Cheers,<br/>
  The Piessang Team
</p>
